                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                  <locus target="#2r"/>
                                  <desc type="GuestText">Instead of the erased half of the chant in honor of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6819Mary">St Mary</persName> there is a hymn in honor of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4306GabraMa">Gabra Manfas Qǝddus</persName>.</desc>
                                  <q xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ጻድቅ፡ ሰረገላከ፡ መብረቅ፡ ቅናትከ፡ ጋጋ፡ ወልብስከ፡ ሰቅ፡</q>
