                                  <note>
                                 <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/T6UTP6JE"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Turaev1906rukopisi"/><title level="m">Ėfiopskija rukopisi v S.-Peterburgě</title><title level="s">Pamjatniki ėfiopskoj pis'mennosti</title><author><forename>Boris</forename><surname>Turaev</surname></author><pubPlace>St Petersburg</pubPlace><publisher>Tipografija imperatorskoj Akademii Nauk</publisher><date>1906</date><series><title level="s">Pamjatniki ėfiopskoj pis'mennosti</title><biblScope unit="volume">3</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">3</biblScope><note type="url">http://digitale-sammlungen.ulb.uni-bonn.de/content/titleinfo/2104581</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:Turaev1906rukopisi</note></note><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:Turaev1906rukopisi</note><citedRange unit="page">89</citedRange></bibl> gives his regnal name Wanāg Sagad, and identifies him with Minās.</note>
